hackathon-description-text: Spectra is a brand-new women's hackathon in the west coast!

hackathon-judges.judge-role: Software Engineer on YouTube Player Infrastructure

hackathon-requirements: Please have one teammate sign up your team to enter for prizes!

hackathon-prizes.prize-content: Every teammate will receive a Nexus 6p.
Each teammate will receive a Chromebook.
Each teammate present will receive a Chromecast.
Each teammate present will receive a Chromecast Audio.
Each teammate present will receive Goggle tech VR glasses.
Each teammate present will receive Bose headphones.
Each team member will get a YouTube water bottle.
